help me fly?

1474
01:51:49,286 --> 01:51:50,536
That's the plan.

1475
01:51:51,204 --> 01:51:52,662
Think you can work out...

1476
01:52:00,421 --> 01:52:01,421
Okay.

1477
01:52:02,800 --> 01:52:05,226
Clearly some aptitude for the...

1478
01:52:07,429 --> 01:52:09,971
It ain't all buttons and charts, little albatross.

1479
01:52:10,390 --> 01:52:12,516
You know what the first rule of flying is?

1480
01:52:13,018 --> 01:52:16,020
Well, I suppose you do, since you already
know what I'm about to say.

1481
01:52:17,064 --> 01:52:18,122
I do.

1482
01:52:19,690 --> 01:52:21,442
But I like to hear you say it.

1483
01:52:26,198 --> 01:52:27,239
Love.

1484
01:52:27,573 --> 01:52:29,449
You can learn all the math in the 'verse,

1485
01:52:29,534 --> 01:52:31,577
but you take a boat
in the air that you don't love,

1486
01:52:31,662 --> 01:52:34,497
she'll shake you off just as sure
as the turn of the worlds.

1487
01:52:37,835 --> 01:52:40,444
Love keeps her in the air when
she ought to fall down,

1488
01:52:42,005 --> 01:52:44,340
tells you she's hurting before she keels.

1489
01:52:47,136 --> 01:52:48,344
Makes her a home.

1490
01:52:53,975 --> 01:52:55,851
Storm's getting worse.

1491
01:52:58,146 --> 01:53:00,157
